= Device Drivers (`kernel/drivers`)
:toc: left
:icons: font
:sectlinks:

See also: link:index.html[Kernel Index], link:fs.html[Filesystem], link:sys.html[System Services]

This directory contains device drivers for storage, input, and terminal output, including ATA/FDC disk access, keyboard handling, and TTY rendering.

== Summary

* Hardware-facing implementations for block and character devices.
* TTY subsystem handles kernel/user text output to VGA-backed console.
* Keyboard path provides input events into terminal line discipline.

== Typical Work in This Area

* Add or improve hardware support.
* Debug IRQ-driven input/output behavior.
* Extend terminal and console capabilities.

